    public class DefaultView
extends javax.swing.JFrame
implements IView
    A view as in MVC.

    This view instantiates

    • a MenuBar
    • a ToolBar
    • a GraphPanel
    • a controller panel with a AlgorithmPanel and a TraversalPanel
    Author:
    Roland Bruggmann (brugr9@bfh.ch)
